RESEARCH_MUNICIPALITY.notes: Cheney, WA operates under a strong mayor-council government. Elsa Martin appears to have secured the position of Mayor in the November 2025 election, though results are unofficial until certified on November 25, 2025. The City Council consists of seven members elected at large. The winner for City Council Position 4 in the November 2025 election was not definitively stated in the available unofficial results as of November 18, 2025, with Rebecca Long leading by a narrow margin.
